    <section id="thecourses" class="container thecourses"> 
     <h2>My Favorite Course</h2> 
     <blockquote>
      <p>“Ancient Greek was my favorite because they were tiny classes that John Lenz was teaching. There was a lot of individual attention and it was awesome learning a language that almost no one knows anymore.”</p>
     </blockquote> 
