           <section class="core"> 
            <header>
             <h2>Requirements for the Minor (20 credits)</h2>
            </header> 
            <p>20intermediate or upper-levelcredits in Classics or related courses, including language courses, and literature, history, or civilization courses in translation, selected in consultation with departmental faculty. Exemption from one course at the intermediate or upper level can be counted toward the minor.</p> 
